parameters:
\n<Dodon>Haah... haah... I don't even have the energy to climb a
ladder and escape. Hahaha!

\n<Rakura>Ugh, out of magical power... Looks like this is it for me.
Sorry! I'm dead.

\n<Annie>Ah, I can't go on either. I'm out of strength... To think
I'd end up dying here with you guys. Well, it was pretty
fun, Dodon. Rakura.
\n<Prim>Hmm...? Do you feel a sinister presence?

\n<Terra>What! So you had it from the start. To think you were
casting a barrier and sealing away the magical power. Haah,
I was worried you were blown to smithereens.

\n<Terra>Well then, let's go ahead and massacre the rest of the
villagers...

\n<Annie>Rui! The town's in chaos! We've evacuated everyone who can't
fight! But there are monsters in the residential area
too...! Damn it! Why is this happening all of a sudden!!
\n<Rakura>Why won't you die already! You monster...!

\n<Dodon>Damn it! What the hell is this all of a sudden!! Hey! Rui!
It's an attack! Kill the monsters!!

\n<Dodon>Ahh!? Rui!? Not looking, huh?! Maybe they're fighting
somewhere else! You protect the town too!

\n<Dodon>Ahh!? Ones!? Not looking, huh?! Maybe they're fighting
somewhere else! You protect the town too!
There's no response. It seems they've already passed away.
There's no response. It seems they've already passed away.
